<p>I am a postdoctoral research fellow at the University of Exeter. I work in the field of Comparative Politics, specifically the comparative studies of political institutions and the comparative studies of electoral systems.
I study such phenomena as</p>

<ul>
  <li>institutional and non-institutional determinants of electoral behaviour</li>
  <li>electoral coordation</li>
  <li>organisational stability of political parties</li>
  <li>party system institutionalisation</li>
  <li>interplay between formal and informal institutions</li>
  <li>the integrating role of parties in federations</li>
</ul>
